    "description": "Join the Cleartrip Ventures Solutions family as a SEO Specialist in Pimpri-Chinchwad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Cleartrip Ventures Solutions:\nCleartrip Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Cleartrip Ventures Solutions!",
